{
  "stem": "19550.9",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I was-- when I left the-- the hospital in Tutzing-- as I said, I went to Feldafing-- and participated in organizing and managing the camp under the authority of the military government.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, also, I volunteered my services to the Americans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in one instance at least, I-- I think I-- I rendered some real service, at the-- on behalf of the CIC, or what they-- the-- the counterintelligence service.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Together with a friend, I managed to get ahold of the last camp commander we had, Oberscharfuhrer Meyer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- we captured him in Starnberg and brought him down to the counterintelligence service.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't an easy matter, because my-- my friend felt that the best treatment we could mete out to him would be to literally throw him down the mountain.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I finally succeeded in persuading him that we had better not be lawless.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's the lawlessness of the world that we suffered from.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I wasn't about to-- to become lawless or to inflict it on even a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then at the camp, I had participated in providing the camp with food and clothing and supplies, which we could, with the authority of-- of the military government, requisition, obtain, and purchase.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] also in creating a cultural life for-- for the camp, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we had all-- all sorts of things that we did, particularly performances of all kinds.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Very quickly, people of talent came forward or appeared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we even managed at one time to take some of the scenery from the Munich opera.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and we had a performance of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] put on in-- in Feldafing.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
